OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779624668
OL,3,CMan rejected from army over mild
OL,4,Casthma calls for change to recruitment
OL,5,Cprocess
OL,7,FA young man from Dorset is calling for
OL,8,Fchange, after his application to join
OL,9,Fthe army was rejected due to a
OL,10,Fchildhood illness.
OL,12,FBen Smith, 19, says it has been his
OL,13,Fdream to serve in the armed forces,
OL,14,Fand the way they recruit needs to
OL,15,Fadapt.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779624668
OL,3,CMan rejected from army over mild
OL,4,Casthma calls for change to recruitment
OL,5,Cprocess
OL,7,FThousands of people have had their
OL,8,Fapplications rejected for similar
OL,9,Freasons in the past few years, and it
OL,10,Fappears that the Ministry of Defence
OL,11,Fis now taking notice of cases where
OL,12,Fpotential recruits are denied a job -
OL,13,Ffor what many consider minor or
OL,14,Fhistoric ailments.
OL,16,FOver the course of a year and a half,
OL,17,FBen Smith was rejected by the Army,
OL,18,Fthe RAF and the Navy due to a "mild"
OL,19,Fasthma condition.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779624668
OL,3,CMan rejected from army over mild
OL,4,Casthma calls for change to recruitment
OL,5,Cprocess
OL,7,FHe told ITV Meridian he has wanted to
OL,8,Fjoin the armed forces his whole life.
OL,10,FBen said: "I cried. It's not something
OL,11,Fyou want to hear. A dream since I was
OL,12,Fthree years old. An automated email.
OL,13,FIt's not human.
OL,15,F"We are asking people to do a job, to
OL,16,Fput lives on the line and I want to do
OL,17,Fthat.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779624668
OL,3,CMan rejected from army over mild
OL,4,Casthma calls for change to recruitment
OL,5,Cprocess
OL,7,F"I use my inhaler once before I go to
OL,8,Fbed and once when I wake up. I don't
OL,9,Fknow why because of that I can't join
OL,10,Fthe army."
OL,12,FMany medical conditions can prevent a
OL,13,Fmilitary career, including chronic
OL,14,Fback pain, migraines or diabetes. A
OL,15,Fserious food allergy or poor dental
OL,16,Fhygiene could mean a failed
OL,17,Fapplication.
OL,19,FFor a variety of reasons, recruitment
OL,20,Fhas been an issue for the armed forces
OL,21,Ffor many years.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779624668
OL,3,CMan rejected from army over mild
OL,4,Casthma calls for change to recruitment
OL,5,Cprocess
OL,7,FThe current Conservative shadow
OL,8,Fminister for defence admits mistakes
OL,9,Fwere made and says he is keen to make
OL,10,Famends.
OL,12,FJames Cartlidge MP said: "My sense is
OL,13,Fthat we probably are being too strict.
OL,14,FThe challenge is how do you maintain a
OL,15,Ftough barrier to get over because we
OL,16,Fwant the best people in the armed
OL,17,Fforces, but be more open minded.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779624668
OL,3,CMan rejected from army over mild
OL,4,Casthma calls for change to recruitment
OL,5,Cprocess
OL,7,F"And the way we are going to do that
OL,8,Fis a policy review. I'll be speaking
OL,9,Fto experts in the private sector and
OL,10,Fin the military so we have a more
OL,11,Fattractive way of getting people in
OL,12,Fthe armed forces."
OL,14,FIn a statement, a Ministry of Defence
OL,15,Fspokesperson said: "The government has
OL,16,Fchanged the rules so that those who
OL,17,Fhave had asthma can serve in the armed
OL,18,Fforces following medical examination.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779624668
OL,3,CMan rejected from army over mild
OL,4,Casthma calls for change to recruitment
OL,5,Cprocess
OL,7,F"This is part of our work to reversing
OL,8,Fthe four-year decline in Armed Forces
OL,9,Frecruitment, which includes scrapping
OL,10,Fover 100 outdated policies and
OL,11,Fspeeding up the process for those
OL,12,Fwishing to rejoin the military.
OL,14,F"More personnel are now joining the
OL,15,Fmilitary than leaving, for the first
OL,16,Ftime since 2020.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779624668
OL,3,CMan rejected from army over mild
OL,4,Casthma calls for change to recruitment
OL,5,Cprocess
OL,7,F"We are unable to discuss individual
OL,8,Fcases, but every application is
OL,9,Fconsidered on a case-by-case basis by
OL,10,Fspecialist clinicians, and hearing or
OL,11,Frespiratory conditions, such as
OL,12,Fasthma, are not an automatic basis for
OL,13,Frejection."
OL,15,FThe recruitment rethink could be good
OL,16,Fnews for Ben who said: "Obviously
OL,17,Fthere is some encouragement for me. I
OL,18,Fam still very much wanting to join the
OL,19,Fmilitary and if I get the chance I
OL,20,Fwill join up straight away."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
