PN,41609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779624668
OL,3,CMan rejected from army over mild
OL,4,Casthma calls for change to recruitment
OL,5,Cprocess
OL,7,FA new recruitment system will be in
OL,8,Fplace by 2027, which the government
OL,9,Fpromises will require just one medical
OL,10,Fevaluation and a more straightforward
OL,11,Fprocess to join the armed forces.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/9
